#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Kronometer"
msgstr "Kronometer"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Chronometer"
msgstr "Tietmeter"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:14
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Kronometer is a stopwatch application built for the KDE Desktop "
#| "Environment. It features the basic stopwatch actions (pause/resume/reset/"
#| "laps), as well as the ability to save the times on a file and resume them "
#| "later. Kronometer is part of the KDE Extragear collection, within the "
#| "Utils sub-module."
msgid ""
"Kronometer is a stopwatch application. It features the basic stopwatch "
"actions (pause/resume/reset/laps), as well as the ability to save the times "
"and resume them later. Kronometer is part of the KDE Extragear collection, "
"within the Utils sub-module."
msgstr ""
"Kronometer is en Stoppklock-Programm för den KDE-Schriefdisch. Dat hett de "
"normalen Stoppklock-Funkschonen (anhollen, wiedermaken, torüchsetten, "
"Runnen), man kann de Tieden ok sekern un dor later mit wiedermaken. "
"Kronometer is Deel vun de de KDE-Extragear-Sammeln, binnen dat Warktüüch-"
"Ünnermoduul."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:17
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Markmalen:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:19
msgid "Start/pause/resume the stopwatch widget"
msgstr "Anfangen, anhollen un wiedermaken över dat Stoppklock-Lüttprogramm"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:20
msgid "Laps recording: you can capture the stopwatch time when you want"
msgstr ""
"Runnen opnehmen: Du kannst de Stoppklock-Tiet aflesen, wenn Du dat wullt"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:21
msgid ""
"Lap times sorting: you can easily find the shortest lap time or the longest "
"one"
msgstr ""
"Runnentieden sorteren: Du kannst de körtste oder de längste Runntiet heel "
"eenfach rutfinnen"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:22
msgid "Reset the stopwatch widget and the lap times"
msgstr "Dat Stoppklock-Lüttprogramm un de Runnentieden torüchsetten"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:23
msgid "Time format settings: you can choose the stopwatch granularity"
msgstr "Tietformaat instellen: Du kannst de Oplösen vun de Stoppklock utsöken"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:24
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Times saving and resuming: you can save the stopwatch status on a file "
#| "and resume it later"
msgid ""
"Times saving and resuming: you can save the stopwatch status and resume it "
"later"
msgstr ""
"Tieden sekern un wedder opnehmen: Du kannst de Stoppklockweerten sekern un "
"later dor mit wiedermaken"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:25
msgid ""
"Font customization: you can choose the fonts for each of the stopwatch digits"
msgstr ""
"Schrift topassen: Du kannst de Schrift för elkeen Tall op de Stoppklock "
"utsöken"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:26
msgid ""
"Color customization: you can choose the color for the stopwatch digits and "
"the stopwatch background"
msgstr ""
"Klöör topassen: Du kannst de Klöör för de Stoppklock-Tallen un de "
"Achtergrundklöör utsöken."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kronometer.appdata.xml:27
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Lap times export: you can export the lap times on a file using the XML or "
